Name: Emergency
FSL__Description__c: This policy is used in order to schedule emergencies from the emergency action

Name: Reduce Travel
FSL__Description__c: SLA to be respected and reduction of travel time

Name: Focus on Service Request
FSL__Description__c: High level of priority. When in conflict with Maintenance WO, SR would get the priority

Name: Limited Resource
FSL__Description__c: Less resources with a re-evaluation of work order priorities.

Name: Customer First
FSL__Description__c: This policy balances great customer service with travel minimization. Appointments are graded first by the customer\'s selection of a preferred employee and by the ability to provide the service as soon as possible. Travel minimization is considered as a second priority.
